Title: Pharmacokinetics of cannabinoids.

Sentece: Nabilone is well absorbed and the pharmacokinetics, although variable, appear to be linear from oral doses of 1 mg to 4 mg (these doses show a plasma elimination half-life of approximately 2 h).
Title: Pharmacokinetics of cannabinoids.
Name: Nabilone

Sentece: The absorbed drug disappeared from plasma rather rapidly (half-life, approximately 2 hr), evidently due to extensive tissue distribution and rapid metabolism.
Title: Physiologic disposition of nabilone, a cannabinol derivative, in man.
Name: Nabilone

Sentece: The metabolites of nabilone persist in plasma for extended periods (half-life of total radioactivity exceeds 20 hr).
